org.ServerGui.Controller

Class AbstractSceneController

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ServerGui.Controller.AbstractSceneController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AssignPlayersSceneController, AssignPlayersTournamentSceneController, ConfigSceneController, CreateGameSceneController, CreateTournamentSceneController, LobbySceneController, NewOrSavedGameSceneController, NewOrSavedTournamentSceneController, RankingSceneController, SelectWinnerSceneController

    public abstract class AbstractSceneController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable

    Every Scene created needs its own Controller for its GUI. This class implements Initializable to initialize its Controller. For a new SceneController, one simply needs to extend this class and implement all needed method(given by the Initializable Interface).
